verbose_text: Previous studies have shown that CXCR4 contributes to the quiescence of a primitive hematopoietic stem cell, and CXCR4 -/- can lead to an abnormal proliferation of hematopoietic stem cells and disturb hematopoietic system steady state [XREF_BIBR].
evidence: CXCR4 -/-  can lead to an abnormal proliferation
